A home is not a commodity. It is a slow accumulation of intention &mdash;
              of rooms that know what they are for, of materials that age with grace,
              of light that lands the way it should.
</p> <p class="mt-10 max-w-2xl text-mist text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
Ikena begins every project the way it ends: with care, restraint, and
              an insistence that the work be worthy of the place it occupies. Laulima &mdash;
              many hands, one build. We are a small practice by choice. Two projects
              at a time. One standard.
</p> </div> </div> </astro-slot></div><!--astro:end--></astro-island> </div> </section> <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-ink via-koa/10 to-ink py-28 md:py-40 border-t border-paper/5"> <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-6 md:px-10"> <astro-island uid="Z1VbRYY" prefix="r9" component-url="/_astro/Reveal.BWQsqrWn.js" component-export="default" renderer-url="/_astro/client.mxV3x1Xx.js" props="{}" ssr client="visible" opts="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Reveal&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:true}" await-children><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px)"><astro-slot> <div class="mb-20 md:mb-28 max-w-2xl"> <div class="eyebrow mb-6">Approach</div> <h2 class="text-paper text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-[1.1]">
