384,262 statewide TMK parcels, 239,458 Honolulu building
              footprints with real heights, 204,775 address points &mdash;
              encoded as TypeScript, served as a 3D map. So we always know
              what we&rsquo;re standing on.
</p> <a href="https://maps.ikenagroup.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="eyebrow link-underline text-paper inline-block">maps.ikenagroup.com &rarr;</a> </div> <div class="space-y-4 md:mt-12"> <div class="text-mist text-sm tracking-[0.2em]">02 &mdash; ProBuildCalc</div> <h3 class="text-paper text-2xl md:text-3xl">LiDAR scans, native.</h3> <p class="text-mist text-sm leading-relaxed">
Our iOS measuring app uses Apple&rsquo;s RoomPlan + Object
              Capture to scan a room or an object on-site, then drops it
              straight into the project portal. No Polycam wrapper.
              No subscription tax.
</p> <span class="eyebrow text-mist inline-block">In private TestFlight</span> </div> <div class="space-y-4 md:mt-24"> <div class="text-mist text-sm tracking-[0.2em]">03 &mdash; Project portal</div> <h3 class="text-paper text-2xl md:text-3xl">Plans, scans, change orders &mdash; one view.</h3> <p class="text-mist text-sm leading-relaxed">
Every Ikena client gets a private space at portal.ikenagroup.com:
              live blueprints, scanned 3D models, daily logs, AIA-grade
              invoices, selections, change orders. Not a SaaS rental &mdash;
              ours, end to end.
</p> <a href="https://portal.ikenagroup.com" class="eyebrow link-underline text-paper inline-block">portal.ikenagroup.com &rarr;</a> </div> </div> </astro-slot></div><!--astro:end--></astro-island> </div> </section> <section class="relative py-40 md:py-56 overflow-hidden border-t border-paper/5"> <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0"> <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519834584171-e5f0dd01268b?q=80&w=2400&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30"> <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-ink via-ink/70 to-ink"></div> </div> <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[1100px] px-6 md:px-10 text-center"> <astro-island uid="zhsr2" prefix="r15" component-url="/_astro/Reveal.BWQsqrWn.js" component-export="default" renderer-url="/_astro/client.mxV3x1Xx.js" props="{}" ssr client="visible" opts="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Reveal&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:true}" await-children><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px)"><astro-slot> <div class="eyebrow mb-8">Begin</div> <h2 class="text-paper text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-[1.1] mb-10" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
